# Contact form (Web3Forms) — delivers submissions to the inbox tied to the key.
# Get a free access key at https://web3forms.com by entering the destination
# email (Lunamardigital1@outlook.com), then paste the key below.
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill it in. NEXT_PUBLIC_ vars are exposed
# to the browser, which is expected for the Web3Forms client-side key.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
